Package ie.gmit.sw.Reflection

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ListClassable
    An Interface that contains all declarative methods required by the ListClass class.
    Metricable
    An Interface that contains all declarative methods required by the CalculateMetrics class.
    Metricator
    An Interface that contains all declarative methods required by the Metric class.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CalculateMetrics
    A class that is used to calculate the Afferent and Efferent couplings and Stability of a given class / jar file.
    JarFileName
    A class that holds the value of a given jar file name in String format.
    ListClass
    A Customised List class that implements the ListClassable interface and delegates calls to the java.util.list package, which performs a number of required operations.
    Metric
    A 'Bean' class that contains Getters and Setters for a given Metric object.
    MetricFactory
    A Factory class that creates a Single instance of the Metric class.
    ObjectMapAdapter
    A Class that holds a single method that takes in a Map and returns a 2d Object Array and takes both a required Map and a Metric Object as arguments.
    ReadJarFileData
    A Class used to read the contents of a given Jar File into a List.
    TestRunner
    Created to fully test the application and display the results in the console.
